有啲奇怪<br />\n又話香港係蟈一部份<br />\n咁本身喺入面就唔洗話我的家在蟈啦<br />\n係個人唔喺蟈先要講我的家在蟈啫，例如，局長仔女咁<br />\n應該派去澳洲合理過喺香港港派喎"},{"pid":"fff0e036a590420447a75b36521aee00f43eadea","tid":2455890,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"會唔會有人整D網上反洗腦教材呢<br />\nBTW係香港整都危險<br />\n可能要外國手足整"},{"pid":"0ef6bb4e72054c2ff46778ec0869b12f137950a3","tid":2455890,"uid":59158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:24:12.000Z","msg":"你個仆街仔係邊撚度呀家陣<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a61b3f37d6bc228f4c0b17b4045771b28fdbe9","tid":2455890,"uid":74361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:27:07.000Z","msg":"而家諗兩諗一國兩制根本就係想港毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63a002110ac599507162d4c1a09320bdb62df7b","tid":2455890,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"佢全家係澳洲wor"},{"pid":"e4b672f5e60669bd55b402233953110e385456ff","tid":2455890,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:29:40.000Z","msg":"外國籍嘅係咪可以唔上？"},{"pid":"d80a4729332989b6eced1d56b2089bb8f29d394d","tid":2455890,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPZ6AEw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPZ6AEw.gif&h=935ebfd2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJNzKxR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJNzKxR.gif&h=60379894&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gfnjVEx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgfnjVEx.gif&h=57c85e32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1